snippet.title: Guilty Alice's [Full Buy - Game Died 3/17/20] the Joker's Route - Alice End [+3CG Scenes]
snippet.description:
[I won't release publicly too much of this one, because the routes are available still in a fashion on Story Jar now...It's not the same as my old full buy app though and I completely released the Event Stories/Mad Hatter Route & Joker Route on my other channel by now]

This was by SWD, a full buy game and I completely finished up 17 games by them. I'll start releasing them now that it's been about 2 years since they were discontinued and out of print.


[Other Games 'Are Now On Main Channel', sub there for them too.] I have  the url in my bio. 

I update weekly here now that I'm off hiatus and was on the Hub in discord we built, if you want to turn on notifications. [I cover out of print JP otome Alice games we never saw here in eng too. Translating them and other Quinrose games on both channels. ]

Join Our Private Discord 
https://discord.gg/C3tHS2C
(Sub and DM me proof, I'll add you for the access to stuff I'm still editing and can't post publicly yet. Also,  feel free to promote yourself there in correct tabs.)Thx!
